snippet.title: Base Commander Alpha Gameplay Footage
snippet.description:
Base Commander is a 5v5 MOBA coming soon on Steam. Work with your team to capture, or steal, bases that grant power ups like attack damage, speed, ghost powers, and more! 

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1900960/Base_Commander/#:~:text=Base%20Commander%20on%20Steam&text=A%205v5%20MOBA%20where%20players,control%20of%20uniquely%20powered%20bases.

Discord: 
https://discord.gg/basecommander
